    "text": [
        "Dear sir or madam,",
        "",
        "I am a regular reader of your magazine and I have always liked the articles published by you. However, one article which I read today has incorrect information about my city.",
        "",
        "The original name of my city is Pratishtana pur from which the current name \u2018Phaltan\u2019 was derived in the year 1948, but the article mentions the wrong year which is 1970.",
        "",
        "I am very proud of our historical place and people have the right to know the correct information about our ancient town. I was quite surprised to read wrong details and stunned with the fact that the article was published without any research or fact checking.",
        "",
        "I would like to make a humble request to correct the information in the next article with an apology to people whose feelings were hurt by wrong information. I would also like to urge you to check the facts before publication.",
        "",
        "I am looking forward to seeing the corrected article in the near future.",
        "Yours faithfully,",
        "Meenu Sharma."
    ],
